** Emphasis

<pre>
<verbatim>

  *bold*
  /italics/
  _underline_
  _/underlineitalics/_
  _*underlinebold*_

  In the current gnus configuration (font selection) bolditalics is
  the same as bold.

  */bolditalics/*
  _*/underlinebolditalics/*_

</verbatim>
